quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,74,"Monkae εberε a Ɔyεε mo ananmusifoͻ wͻ Aadfoͻ no akyi, de mo tenaa asaase no soͻ, na mosisii mo abansoroͻ wͻ ne petee no mu, san bͻne mmepͻ mu yεε no adan. Enti monkae Nyankopͻn adom, na monhwε yie na moanni nsεmͻnee wͻ asaase no so."
  7,75,"Nhemfo (anaa mpanimfoͻ) a wͻyε ahomasoͻ wͻ ne nkorͻfoͻ no mu no ka kyerεε wͻn a wͻyε mmrε na wͻagye adi wͻ wͻn mu no sε: “Monim sε Soalh yε obia ne Wura Nyankopͻn na asoma no? “Wͻkaa sε: “Nokorε sε yεgye deε yεde asoma no no di”."
  7,76,"Wͻn a wͻyε ahomasoͻ no kaa sε: “Nokorε sε yε deε, yεnnye deε mogye die no nni “."
  7,77,"Enti wͻkum yoma bedeε no, na wͻtee wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn ahyεdeε no so atua, kaa sε: “Soalh, fa deε wahyε yεn ho bͻ no bra, sε woka (Nyame) asomafoͻ no ho ampa a”."
  7,78,"Enti asaase wosoͻ sͻͻ wͻn mu, na wͻyεε dinn wͻ wͻn afie mu."
  7,79,"Enti (Soalh) danee ne ho firii wͻn ho kaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, mebͻͻ mo me Wura Nyankopͻn Asεm no ho dawuro kyerεε mo, na metuu mo fo, nanso moampε afotuo no”."
  7,80,"Ɛna Lut nso, εberε a ͻka kyerεε ne nkorͻfoͻ no sε: “Mobͻ ahohwi bra a amansan no mu biara nnii moanim kan nyεε bi da?”"
  7,81,"“Nokorε sε, mofiri mmaa akyi de akͻnnͻ kͻ mmarima ho. Daabi, moyε nnipa a modi nsεmᴐne.”"
